descriptionHtml:
[size=5][img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/83717-1-1494133302.jpg[/img]Hi darudes! <3

New enb, new life, new b*tchies!

hope you guys liked it ![/size]


[size=6]Installation:[/size] 
[size=5]1)[/size] Download the latest version of enbseries here: http://enbdev.com/download_mod_tesskyrim.html
      copy and paste everything for the WrapperVersion in your skyrim folder. 

[size=5]2)[/size]After that, download my file and copy and paste everything inside of ''borsalino enb'' to your Skyrim folder. 

[size=5]3)[/size]Add this to your [Display] option in "SkyrimPrefs.ini" but if you already have it just change the 0 to 1.

   bFloatPointRenderTarget=1
   bTreesReceiveShadows=1
   bDrawLandShadows=1
   bShadowsOnGrass=1

[size=5]4)[/size] Active all .esp files


[size=5]5)[/size] [b]u are good to go![/b] xD 

[size=5]6) [/size]You [b][size=6]NEED[/size][/b] this mod to have a better view: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/58212/?
